      "content": "hey, i'm prepping for a debate tournament and im stuck on my opening statement. if you had to say which side of the illegal immigration debate is actually more morally defensible—is it the argument for strict border security/national sovereignty or the argument for humanitarian asylum and human rights? like, which one has the stronger moral ground?",
